      <h1>The Philosophy of Great Leadership: What It Really Means to Lead Well</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">Leadership is not a title — it is a philosophy practiced daily. Explore what the greatest thinkers and most effective leaders say about what it actually means to lead people well.</p>
